PROXIMITY_IMMEDIATE - Static variable in class com.chaione.contexthub.sdk.beacons.IBeacon

PROXIMITY_NEAR - Static variable in class com.chaione.contexthub.sdk.beacons.IBeacon

PROXIMITY_UNKNOWN - Static variable in class com.chaione.contexthub.sdk.beacons.IBeacon
